fair; Los Angeles 63 cloudy; Phoenix 93 fair; Salt Lake City 71
fair; San Diego 67 cloudy; San Francisco 55 fair; Seattle 65 fair.
   _Canada: Montreal 73 fair; Toronto 68 fair.
