<HEAD>Girl is Set on Fire, But Gives Birth</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: Leads with 1 graf to UPDATE with hospital now saying girl burned
over 70 percent of body, sted 85 percent; INSERTS 1 graf after 4th graf,
`Hospital officials ..., to UPDATE with details on condition. Pick up 5th
